solution.p:
For each case, you must use the recurrence to find f(1)\text{,} f(2) ... f(4)\text{.}  But notice each time you just add 9 to the previous.  We do this 4 times. 




f(4) = 37\text{.}




f(4) = 38\text{.}




f(4) = 55\text{.}




f(4) = 197\text{.}

